    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/e83aeec6496e3f1b36a1c239ef41b1c4.poster.avif?t=1767564246\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/e83aeec6496e3f1b36a1c239ef41b1c4.webm?t=1767564246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/e83aeec6496e3f1b36a1c239ef41b1c4.mp4?t=1767564246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real-Time Strategy Returns on a Larger Scale.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/3435a39340a36b6517e44c6765597124.avif?t=1767564246\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras_big/3435a39340a36b6517e44c6765597124.avif?t=1767564246 width=800 height=450 /></span>Apoceus: Winter Wars is a fantasy real-time strategy game that focuses on bringing back all the classical elements from the past, such as resource gathering, recruiting &amp; controlling armies, and base building, but on a much bigger scale.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Large Scale</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Base Building &amp; R</i>esource<i> gathering</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Fantasy</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Multiplayer</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/3fd449a8faeac30044b072afe1bdaffa.poster.avif?t=1767564246\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/3fd449a8faeac30044b072afe1bdaffa.webm?t=1767564246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/3fd449a8faeac30044b072afe1bdaffa.mp4?t=1767564246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We believe that base building and resource gathering have always been the core pillars of an exciting RTS experience. In <i>Apoceus: Winter Wars</i>, we’re bringing back that classic feeling you know and love and enchant it on a scale that has never been seen in a fantasy RTS before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/108bf1eb7280a84e36a676df466beee8.poster.avif?t=1767564246\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/108bf1eb7280a84e36a676df466beee8.webm?t=1767564246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/108bf1eb7280a84e36a676df466beee8.mp4?t=1767564246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your <span class=\"bb_strike\">unit</span>, <span class=\"bb_strike\">units</span>, <span class=\"bb_strike\">groups</span>, ARMIES of hundreds (with a goal of thousands) of unique single entities and lead them into devastating battles in multiplayer to annihilate your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/e0bd3a464ca45877f2b4a6e160b195d6.poster.avif?t=1767564246\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/e0bd3a464ca45877f2b4a6e160b195d6.webm?t=1767564246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/e0bd3a464ca45877f2b4a6e160b195d6.mp4?t=1767564246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Select one of three possible generals, each with their own unique traits and units. The goal is to annihilate your enemy's general by any means necessary.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/d69d4d8ed677bafb0411fcb9a7943bf5.poster.avif?t=1767564246\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/d69d4d8ed677bafb0411fcb9a7943bf5.webm?t=1767564246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/d69d4d8ed677bafb0411fcb9a7943bf5.mp4?t=1767564246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Apoceus: Winter Wars we take scale even further, in the final version. you will be able to control enormous units, known as Titans and lay waste to your enemies.<br>Each General will come with their own unique Titan. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/bc306e8c71433cafd7dee7c47544b478.avif?t=1767564246\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras_big/bc306e8c71433cafd7dee7c47544b478.avif?t=1767564246 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We want you for RTS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are a small indie studio, and we want to create <i>Apoceus: Winter Wars</i> together with our beloved community and devoted real-time strategy enthusiasts from every part of the globe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your voice heard — join our Discord and let's make the best fantasy large-scale RTS game together. ❤️ Wishlist and follow our social media to become a part of our RTS community.</p>",
